title: CBSE Class 12th compartment result likely to be announced tomorrow
text:
CBSE Class 12th compartment result is likely to be announced tomorrow i.e. August 6, 2015. CBSE, on 16th June, mentioned on its website that the result will be declared in the second week of August. However, the board clearly mentioned that it would not be answering queries related to result declaration date.
Around 10,40,368 candidates registered for the class 12th board examination for the year 2014-15 and out of these, as many as 97,404 students were likely to appear in the compartment exam, according to the reports.
XII compartment exams (for all the subjects) were conducted on July 16, 2015.
